<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>お問い合せアプリ - カラフルエディション</title>
    <style>
        /* --- デザインシステム & カラフルトークン --- */
        :root {
            --color-pink: #FF1493;
            --color-orange: #FF8C00;
            --color-yellow: #FFD700;
            --color-green: #32CD32;
            --color-blue: #00BFFF;
            --color-purple: #9400D3;
            --text-dark: #2C3E50;
            --bg-light: #F8F9FA;
            --card-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            --transition-smooth: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
        }

        /* 全体初期化 */
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN', 'Segoe UI', Meiryo, sans-serif;
            -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFE4E1 0%, #E0FFFF 50%, #FAF0E6 100%);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        /* スマホ向けモックアップ枠 */
        .phone-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 412px;
            height: 844px;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            border-radius: 40px;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            position: relative;
            border: 8px solid #222222;
        }

        /* スタイリッシュでカラフルなグラデーションヘッダー */
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--color-pink), var(--color-orange), var(--color-blue), var(--color-purple));
            background-size: 300% 300%;
            animation: colorfulGradient 12s ease infinite;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 20px 16px 16px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        @keyframes colorfulGradient {
            0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
            100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
        }

        /* メインスクロールエリア */
        .scroll-container {
            flex: 1;
            overflow-y: auto;
            background-color: var(--bg-light);
            padding: 16px;
            padding-bottom: 90px; /* ナビゲーション用の余白 */
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        /* 画面ごとのトランジション */
        .screen {
            display: none;
            animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease-out forwards;
        }

        .screen.active {
            display: block;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* --- 1. AIに質問画面 (チャットUI) --- */
        .chat-layout {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            height: 610px;
        }

        .chat-scroll {
            flex: 1;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding: 8px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .chat-bubble {
            max-width: 85%;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            font-size: 0.92rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
            position: relative;
        }

        .chat-bubble.bot {
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            align-self: flex-start;
            border-radius: 20px 20px 20px 4px;
            border: 1px solid #E2E8F0;
        }

        .chat-bubble.user {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-blue), var(--color-purple));
            color: #FFFFFF;
            align-self: flex-end;
            border-radius: 20px 20px 4px 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .chat-time {
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            color: #A0AEC0;
            margin-top: 4px;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .chat-bubble.user .chat-time {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        }

        /* ローディングインジケーター */
        .chat-bubble.loading {
            background-color: #F0F4F8;
            border: 1px dashed #CBD5E0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            color: #718096;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .loader-dots {
            display: inline-flex;
            gap: 4px;
        }

        .loader-dots span {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-pink), var(--color-orange));
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: bounce 1.2s infinite ease-in-out;
        }

        .loader-dots span:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
        .loader-dots span:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }

        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-8px); }
        }

        /* 問い合わせへの遷移用ボタン */
        .direct-inquiry-box {
            margin-top: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .btn-direct-link {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-pink), var(--color-orange), var(--color-yellow));
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            padding: 10px 18px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: none;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 20, 147, 0.3);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        .btn-direct-link:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(255, 20, 147, 0.2);
        }

        /* チャットフッター入力 */
        .chat-footer {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #E2E8F0;
            background-color: white;
        }

        .chat-input {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border: 2px solid #E2E8F0;
            border-radius: 24px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            outline: none;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        .chat-input:focus {
            border-color: var(--color-blue);
        }

        .chat-send-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-blue), var(--color-purple));
            border: none;
            color: white;
            padding: 0 16px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.3);
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        .chat-send-btn:active {
            transform: scale(0.92);
        }

        /* --- 2. よくある質問画面 --- */
        .section-title {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin: 20px 0 10px;
            padding-left: 10px;
            border-left: 5px solid;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }
        
        /* セクションごとにカラフルなアクセント */
        .sec-join { border-left-color: var(--color-pink); color: var(--color-pink); }
        .sec-content { border-left-color: var(--color-orange); color: var(--color-orange); }
        .sec-level { border-left-color: var(--color-green); color: var(--color-green); }
        .sec-date { border-left-color: var(--color-blue); color: var(--color-blue); }

        .faq-card {
            background: #FFFFFF;
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .faq-card:active {
            transform: scale(0.98);
        }

        .faq-q-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .faq-icon-q {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-pink), var(--color-orange));
            color: white;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .faq-question {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #1A252F;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .faq-toggle {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #A0AEC0;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        .faq-answer {
            margin-top: 12px;
            padding-top: 12px;
            border-top: 1px dashed #E2E8F0;
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            color: #4A5568;
            line-height: 1.5;
            display: none;
            animation: slideDown 0.3s ease-out;
        }

        /* アコーディオン開閉状態 */
        .faq-card.open {
            border-color: rgba(255, 20, 147, 0.3);
        }
        .faq-card.open .faq-toggle {
            transform: rotate(180deg);
            color: var(--color-pink);
        }
        .faq-card.open .faq-answer {
            display: block;
        }

        @keyframes slideDown {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-5px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* --- 3. 問い合わせ画面 --- */
        .form-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #4A5568;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .form-group label::before {
            content: '';
            display: inline-block;
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: var(--color-orange);
        }

        /* 各フォームパーツフォーカス時にカラフルな枠線を適用 */
        .form-input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            border: 2px solid #E2E8F0;
            border-radius: 14px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            outline: none;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            background-color: #F8FAFC;
        }

        .form-input:focus {
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            border-color: var(--color-orange);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.15);
        }

        /* 送信ボタンの超カラフルポップデザイン */
        .btn-submit {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 16px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-pink), var(--color-orange), var(--color-yellow));
            background-size: 200% 100%;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 30px;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(255, 110, 0, 0.35);
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .btn-submit:active {
            transform: scale(0.96);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 12px rgba(255, 110, 0, 0.2);
        }

        /* --- 4. 履歴画面 --- */
        .history-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .history-card:active {
            transform: scale(0.98);
            background-color: #F8FAFC;
        }

        .history-main-info {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
            flex: 1;
        }

        /* カテゴリに応じたカラフル丸型アイコン */
        .history-badge {
            width: 46px;
            height: 46px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .badge-join { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-pink), #FF69B4); }
        .badge-content { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-orange), #FFA500); }
        .badge-level { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-green), #00FF7F); }
        .badge-date { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-blue), #87CEFA); }
        .badge-other { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-purple), #EE82EE); }

        .history-texts {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .history-row-top {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .history-name {
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #1A252F;
        }

        .history-time {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: #A0AEC0;
        }

        .history-category {
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .cat-join-label { background-color: #FFF0F5; color: var(--color-pink); }
        .cat-content-label { background-color: #FFF5EE; color: var(--color-orange); }
        .cat-level-label { background-color: #F0FFF0; color: var(--color-green); }
        .cat-date-label { background-color: #F0F8FF; color: var(--color-blue); }
        .cat-other-label { background-color: #F8F8FF; color: var(--color-purple); }

        .history-detail-summary {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #718096;
            margin-top: 4px;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
            max-width: 220px;
        }

        .history-status-badge {
            font-size: 0.72rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background-color: #E2E8F0;
            color: #4A5568;
        }

        .status-done {
            background-color: #E6FFFA;
            color: #319795;
            border: 1px solid #B2F5EA;
        }

        .status-wait {
            background-color: #FFFAF0;
            color: #DD6B20;
            border: 1px solid #FEEBC8;
        }

        /* 詳細モーダル */
        .modal {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            z-index: 100;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: flex-end;
            opacity: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        .modal.open {
            opacity: 1;
            pointer-events: auto;
        }

        .modal-content {
            width: 100%;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 32px 32px 0 0;
            padding: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 -10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            transform: translateY(100%);
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        .modal.open .modal-content {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .modal-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .modal-title {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .modal-close-btn {
            background: #EDF2F7;
            border: none;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .modal-item {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .modal-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #A0AEC0;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .modal-value {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2D3748;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .modal-reply-box {
            background-color: #F7FAFC;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--color-green);
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
            margin-top: 6px;
        }

        /* --- プレミアム ボトムナビゲーション --- */
        nav {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 74px;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
            padding-bottom: 12px;
            z-index: 20;
        }

        .nav-tab {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #A0AEC0;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 0.72rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            flex: 1;
            height: 100%;
            position: relative;
        }

        .nav-emoji {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        /* タブごとのカラフルなアクティブカラー設計 */
        .nav-tab.active[data-screen="ai"] { color: var(--color-blue); }
        .nav-tab.active[data-screen="ai"] .nav-emoji { transform: scale(1.2); }

        .nav-tab.active[data-screen="faq"] { color: var(--color-pink); }
        .nav-tab.active[data-screen="faq"] .nav-emoji { transform: scale(1.2); }

        .nav-tab.active[data-screen="form"] { color: var(--color-orange); }
        .nav-tab.active[data-screen="form"] .nav-emoji { transform: scale(1.2); }

        .nav-tab.active[data-screen="history"] { color: var(--color-green); }
        .nav-tab.active[data-screen="history"] .nav-emoji { transform: scale(1.2); }

        /* タブの上部にカラフルラインを表示するインジケータ */
        .nav-tab::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            width: 0;
            height: 4px;
            border-radius: 0 0 4px 4px;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        .nav-tab.active[data-screen="ai"]::after { width: 40%; background-color: var(--color-blue); }
        .nav-tab.active[data-screen="faq"]::after { width: 40%; background-color: var(--color-pink); }
        .nav-tab.active[data-screen="form"]::after { width: 40%; background-color: var(--color-orange); }
        .nav-tab.active[data-screen="history"]::after { width: 40%; background-color: var(--color-green); }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="phone-wrapper">
        <!-- グラデーションダイナミックヘッダー（初期画面はAIアシスタントに設定） -->
        <header id="main-header">AIアシスタント</header>

        <!-- メイン画面スクローラー -->
        <div class="scroll-container" id="scroll-wrapper">

            <!-- SCREEN 1: AIに質問画面 (初期起動時にactive) -->
            <div id="screen-ai" class="screen active">
                <div class="chat-layout">
                    <div class="chat-scroll" id="chat-box">
                        <div class="chat-bubble bot">
                            こんにちは！✨AIアシスタントです。研修に関するご不明点やお困りのことがあれば、何でもお気軽に質問してくださいね！💬
                            <div class="chat-time">本日 15:00</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="chat-footer">
                        <input type="text" id="chat-input-text" class="chat-input" placeholder="質問を入力..." onkeypress="handleChatEnter(event)">
                        <button class="chat-send-btn" onclick="sendChatMessage()">✨ 質問する</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- SCREEN 2: よくある質問 (FAQ) -->
            <div id="screen-faq" class="screen">
                <!-- 参加カテゴリ -->
                <div class="section-title sec-join">👉 参加に関する質問</div>
                <div class="faq-card" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                    <div class="faq-q-wrapper">
                        <span class="faq-icon-q">Q</span>
                        <div class="faq-question">誰でも参加できますか？</div>
                        <span class="faq-toggle">▼</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        本研修は公募制となっており、新入社員および既存社員の一部が対象です。募集要項に基づき選考・参加が決定されます。
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 内容カテゴリ -->
                <div class="section-title sec-content">📚 研修内容に関する質問</div>
                <div class="faq-card" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                    <div class="faq-q-wrapper">
                        <span class="faq-icon-q">Q</span>
                        <div class="faq-question">AI×プロダクト開発研修では何を学びますか？</div>
                        <span class="faq-toggle">▼</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        AIにプロダクト開発を任せる手法（バイブコーディング）や、リサーチ・課題設定の進め方を実践的に学びます。
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-card" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                    <div class="faq-q-wrapper">
                        <span class="faq-icon-q">Q</span>
                        <div class="faq-question">リサーチ・課題設定はなぜ重要ですか？</div>
                        <span class="faq-toggle">▼</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        プロダクト開発の初期段階でのリサーチ and 課題設定の質が、その後のアウトプット品質に大きく影響するためです。
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 難易度カテゴリ -->
                <div class="section-title sec-level">💡 難易度・前提スキルについて</div>
                <div class="faq-card" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                    <div class="faq-q-wrapper">
                        <span class="faq-icon-q">Q</span>
                        <div class="faq-question">IT未経験でも参加できますか？</div>
                        <span class="faq-toggle">▼</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
